
### Create a User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "CF_User24",
  "password": "customer",
  "confirmPassword": "customer",
  "email": "coffeeshop24@example.com"
}

### Login in a User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "Habeetech",
  "password": "habeeb-long"
}
